The jQuery Content Tools Extension is planed to become a Framework for many different Content Element Tools, like jQuery UI Elements, Slideshows and much more.

JQCT is being developed and maintained by Andy Hausmann <andy.hausmann@gmx.de>.
Currently, this extension is in an early alpha state and unter heavy development.

When it reaches a notable and functional state of development, it will be uploaded into TER.

